This will suit you well.

624
00:38:34,605 --> 00:38:36,786
Shiyin, please convey my gratitude to your mom.

625
00:38:36,786 --> 00:38:38,378
This is nice.

626
00:38:40,335 --> 00:38:42,235
This one's still better.

627
00:38:50,100 --> 00:38:52,900
Stop playing. We'll be on the stage next. Have you memorized the lines?

628
00:38:52,915 --> 00:38:54,648
Rest assured.

629
00:38:55,305 --> 00:38:57,305
Where's our female lead?

630
00:38:57,305 --> 00:38:59,568
Tang Ya.

631
00:38:59,568 --> 00:39:01,565
Tang... Why are you here?

632
00:39:01,565 --> 00:39:04,585
I'm so nervous, Xue. I'm scared. I...

633
00:39:04,585 --> 00:39:07,875
Relax. They'll be accompanying you.

634
00:39:07,875 --> 00:39:10,275
Come on. Introduce yourselves.

635
00:39:11,005 --> 00:39:14,455
We nearly became classmates before, but I'm too smart.

636
00:39:14,455 --> 00:39:16,275
I was chosen to join the competition class in advance.

637
00:39:16,275 --> 00:39:17,645
Get to the point.

638
00:39:17,645 --> 00:39:20,635
I'm Zhang Qi. I play as Aotian.

639
00:39:20,635 --> 00:39:21,645
Nice to meet you.

640
00:39:21,645 --> 00:39:24,395
I'm Zheng Sunian. I play as Liang Chen.

641
00:39:24,395 --> 00:39:27,168
Hello. I'm Tang Ya.

642
00:39:27,168 --> 00:39:30,525
I play as Princess Jasmine.

643
00:39:30,525 --> 00:39:33,775
- Who's the male lead?
- It's me.
- It's me.

644
00:39:33,775 --> 00:39:36,895
Shao Xue, it's your turn.

645
00:39:36,895 --> 00:39:39,165
Although we haven't had a proper rehearsal,

646
00:39:39,165 --> 00:39:42,515
I believe that our show will amaze everyone in the hall.

647
00:39:42,515 --> 00:39:44,165
Do you have the confidence?

648
00:39:44,165 --> 00:39:45,698
- Yes!
- Yes!

649
00:39:45,698 --> 00:39:47,238
Let's go.

650
00:39:57,225 --> 00:39:59,058
One more time.

651
00:40:07,045 --> 00:40:08,978
Again.

652
00:40:20,775 --> 00:40:22,608
Again.

