00:40:28,558 --> 00:40:30,288
One more time.

655
00:40:30,288 --> 00:40:35,998
Again.

656
00:40:35,998 --> 00:40:37,868
Again!

657
00:40:47,105 --> 00:40:48,738
Stand up.

658
00:40:59,125 --> 00:41:00,858
Again.

659
00:41:02,915 --> 00:41:04,665
Mr. Nai, I'm exhausted.

