00:41:23,195 --> 00:41:26,375
Is it my problem or yours?

664
00:41:26,375 --> 00:41:29,385
Everyone is waiting for you. Are you aware of that?

665
00:41:30,295 --> 00:41:32,145
Do you want to keep dancing

666
00:41:32,145 --> 00:41:35,845
