667
00:41:35,845 --> 00:41:37,788
Say something.

668
00:41:44,005 --> 00:41:45,455
I'll dance.

669
00:41:45,455 --> 00:41:47,288
Good.

670
00:41:47,975 --> 00:41:50,025
Come on. Continue.

671
00:41:50,025 --> 00:41:52,325
You can do it, Shiyin.

672
00:41:57,735 --> 00:41:59,368
Go.

